notes:
The Launcher needs dotnet40 installed to run;

"protontricks 244160 dotnet40"

for some unknown reason, installing dotnet40 once is not enough, you must force install it again and select repair;

"protontricks 244160 --force dotnet40"

That gets the Launcher working, The next issue was the game didn't like my 4K screen resolution, But turning the resolution down got the the game working nicely for me.
The game played fine from then on, but did freeze when clicking the "Exit to desktop" button.
